node.text: Jose Vitor Leme has taken the art of bull riding to the next level. From earning the highest scoring ride in PBR history to shattering the most 90-point outs in a season record, the Champ is putting in a season for the ages. Go behind the chutes as he takes on Show Me Homie for a historic ride ➡️
